<title>
Barbecue Chili Recipe
</title>
<details>
AUTHOR: i heart eating
PREP TIME: 10 minutes
COOK TIME: 1 hour 15 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 1 hour 30 minutes
COURSE: Main Course
CUISINE: American
